<hw>Cha"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., of uncertain
origin.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of flowerless plants,
having articulated stems and whorled branches. They flourish in wet
places.</def>⟦br⟧
